{
  "stem": "17001.7",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she was telling me stories about her brothers, her sisters, her family.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was telling her about my family, and so on.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I introduce her to my other sister, my cousin.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And one day, she comes to me, that I'm very hungry.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I'm together with my sister.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then she told me that this black haired woman who was so mean and cursing, that she's her husband sister.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That that's her sister-in-law.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that she has another sister-in-law with her, and the cousin of the sister-in-law's.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Her husband cousin.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they were four of us, and we were four of us.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So she said, they are very hungry.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And how can I get some food?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I said to her, you know what?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I figured it out already.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was thinking about this.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That when everybody goes to sleep, I will put-- my sister Clara would put the blanket front of the window, because we had windows on the-- on the barrack.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the windows were covered with shutter, with wooden shutter that when they were bombing or so, so that the light shouldn't go out.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I figured it out that if my sister Clara and Elizabeth would hold the blanket over the window, and I would crawl under it, and then I would push the shutter open, providing I listen that when the snow is not crunching, that the German man, the soldier, is not walking by.",
      "word_count": 53
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then I could sneak out and going to the potato [HUNGARIAN].",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "While we were talking, another person overheard us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And she said, I want to be in it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I said to her, no.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because three person is unlucky.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Two person could go and do it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "She insisted that she will tell the [GERMAN] if I don't let her come.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
